collapse: Hides/shows the navbar content on small screens when toggled.
navbar-collapse: Styles the collapsible part of the navbar.
navbar-nav: Styles the <ul> as a horizontal navbar menu.
me-auto: Adds automatic right margin, pushing following elements (like the search form) to the right.
mb-2 mb-lg-0: Adds bottom margin on small screens (mb-2), removes it on large screens (mb-lg-0).
nav-item: Styles each <li> as a navbar item.
nav-link: Styles each <a> as a navbar link.
active: Highlights the current/active link.
dropdown: Enables dropdown behavior for the menu item.
dropdown-toggle: Styles the link to show a dropdown arrow and enables dropdown toggle.
dropdown-menu: Styles the dropdown menu.
dropdown-item: Styles each item in the dropdown.
d-flex: Makes the search form a flex container for horizontal alignment.
form-control: Styles the input as a Bootstrap form field.
btn btn-outline-light: Styles the button with a light outline.



